{"tid":777130,"cid":21,"subCid":3,"title":"cero 「POLY LIFE MULTI SOUL TOUR」debut live in Hong Kong","createTime":"2018-08-12T15:50:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T17:01:22.000Z","uid":79120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6de81aa2bd609fa5da47bfee115aad9d811e4f05","tid":777130,"uid":79120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T15:50:43.000Z","msg":"cero 「POLY LIFE MULTI SOUL TOUR」debut live in Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\n2018年繼The Fin.、Yogee New Waves後，White Noise再帶來另一隊日本樂隊cero。<br />\n<br />\n之所以帶他們來港演出原因有兩個：<br />\n<br />\n1. 他們新作《POLY LIFE MULTI SOUL》，巨著。<br />\n2. 他們龐大陣容的現場演出，精采。<br />\n<br />\n日流回歸，K仔K女都退避三分，不論是老前輩竹內Mariya的《Plastic Love》、松原Miki的《真夜中のドア》，還是新生代Yogee New Waves的《Climax Night》，這些日聽夜聽的洗腦歌都離不開City-Pop，也許不少認識cero都是因為這紅遍全球的曲風，可是他們並非純粹的單一風格，而是混雜不同元素的Eclectic聲音。<br />\n<br />\n以西東京為基地的cero，名字是Contemporary Exotica Rock Orchestra.的簡稱，自從樂隊蛻變成現在的三人行陣容後，音樂也大躍進，高城晶平（主唱、結他、長笛）、荒内佑（鍵琴、和唱）和橋本翼（結他、單簧管、和唱）都是多功能音樂人，三年前第三張專集《Obscure Ride》已逐漸由清爽怡人Guitar-Pop走向多元化，來到今年面世的《POLY LIFE MULTI SOUL》，絕對是登峰造極的巨著，大力加強管弘樂的份量，Guitar-Pop、City-Pop、Reggae、Dub、Soul、Jazz等多面向取材，帶來這張充滿深度的名盤，並登上Oricon公信榜前列，而樂隊這次成熟表現，就像二十前Fishmans的經典《宇宙 日本 世田谷》一樣耀眼。<br />\n<br />\n除了在錄音室，cero也將這豐富的質感帶到現場演出中，今次首度香港舉行音樂會，繼續一絲不茍的認真製作，台上不只cero三人，還會如同日本演出般夥同多位樂手同台玩奏，看Live DVD感受過的無限感染力和張力，置身現場時無疑更精采和熱鬧。<br />\n<br />\n* 預售門票現以於 White Noise Records 獨家發售<br />\n* Advance ticket is now available exclusively at White Noise Records.<br />\n<br />\n** 網上門票現以於 White Noise Records's FB page 網站獨家發售<br />\n** online ticketing is available now at<br />\n** Plus $10.00 HKD service fee<br />\n<br />\nWhite Noise Records: <a href=\"http://www.whitenoiserecords.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitenoiserecords.org&d=l2m5Ikuj4XgffAL1vfCQXtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=bf9d4a22\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.whitenoiserecords.org</a> l <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/WhiteNoiseRec\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FWhiteNoiseRec&d=l2m5Ikuj4XgffAL1vfCQXtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=34d236ed\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/WhiteNoiseRec</a><br />\nPresenter: White Noise<br />\nDesign (Poster): Donmak &amp; Co.<br />\nBackline Equipment support: Backlinestore<br />\nAcknowledgement: Kakubarhythm, Youth Square"},{"pid":"92afa17241b98679c05f2372a242b1d8d1f42b7f","tid":777130,"uid":79120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T15:52:40.000Z","msg":"仲有一個月左右，睇下有無人會去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申飛已買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c00e48b5e621f30328e1b0e9dd21fc1d638c5781","tid":777130,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T15:54:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw,柴灣好遠，做乜唔喺hidden agenda 搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9f99d16d1f8051b553db19af2b0ad33d0d8c347","tid":777130,"uid":79120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c00e48b5e621f30328e1b0e9dd21fc1d638c5781","tid":777130,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T15:54:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw,柴灣好遠，做乜唔喺hidden agenda 搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T15:58:55.000Z","msg":"柴灣堅遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要準時收工先趕得切去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=